cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It may also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) because it involves searching for technical term translations using SMT. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it uses neural networks for machine translation. Finally, it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it involves the use of neural networks for machine translation.
